SUMMARY:Springville Firelane 5 Loop (Trail Run in Forest Park)
DESCRIPTION:Northwest Trail Runners\n**Distance**: 6.2 mile trail run\n**Gain**: 760 feet\n**Start**: Springville Trailhead off Skyline Blvd.\n**After**: Well and Good Cafe (Bonny Slope)\n\nLet’s do a run from one of our favorite trailheads.\nSpringville Rd. Parking can get crowded\, so it’s encouraged to carpool when possible.\n\nThe Route:\nStart heading out Firelane 7\nRight on Trillium\nRight on Wildwood\nLeft onto Firelane 5 (\\~ Mile 2)\, then down and left onto Leif Erikson\nHead north on Leif Erikson to Hardesty (\\~Mile 4)\nLeft on Hardesty\nRight onto Wildwood\nHead North on Wildwood to Springville Rd (\\~Mile 5)\nLeft on Springville\nHead up Springville back to the start\n\nRoute map: https://www.strava.com/routes/3236877116710529782\n\nAfterwards we'll meet for some coffee and good company at\nWell and Good Cafe (Bonny Slope location)\nCafe 11200 NW Thompson Rd\nPortland\, OR 97229\n\nSee you there!\nHosted by: Arne\nNorthwest Trail Runners
